{"tid":1663823,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"90後勇武：有螢光帶但我哋唔係鬼 香港人反抗冇得再輸","createTime":"2019-10-19T16:02:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T17:31:13.000Z","uid":296712,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"1998adf3012a0b2ca5157ac06452b67b9c2faa59","tid":1663823,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"真。朋友代po<br />\n標題我作既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我係一個24歲嘅前線巴打 成日比人話我係阿叔🤷🏻&zwj;♂️因為好嘮叨🤣我係一個混血兒有英國國籍同時我係一個香港人 好多人會話你有國藉怕咩 sorry我唔會離開香港 呢度先係我真正嘅屋企<br />\n<br />\n我前途唔差仲成日俾屋企鬧話我出去咁樣做所有野前途都冇晒(關於工程野）<br />\n但係我地一直堅持自己信念去做<br />\n無論前線又去和理非都好堅守自己有能力崗位 唔好覺得自己上唔到前線冇用 因為你地每一個都好重要<br />\n<br />\n一開始我都係一個超和理非 經過6月頭722嘅痛苦洗禮我決定走上最線<br />\n<br />\n曾經我所有隊員有打算同香港人割蓆 事源101賀佢老母我地係油尖旺最前有螢光X色反光手帶果班 當我地仍然係最前回頭望 啲人話我地係鬼走到同我地距離500米遠 之後防暴係十字路口大街衝出 如果你地打算再賣甩我地 唔會有下次<br />\n<br />\n我知道唔係每一個人都夠膽同popo對疊 但係最少仲有我地呢一班勇武願意繼續行出黎唔怕拉唔怕打唔怕死 比我地年青嘅年青人 你地嘅前途比我地更重要 有時唔好太不自量力被憤怒沖昏自己頭腦 危險意識高啲 經常望下周圍同盡量同認識嘅人組隊<br />\n<br />\n☝🏻試問邊有人唔怕 只係我地呢一班90後願意企最前去守護呢一代同下一代應該擁有嘅權利 哪怕螳臂擋車不自量力 我地好簡單 只要我有能力有手有腳唔怕冇飯食 最怕連自己都放棄自己 <br />\n<br />\n年青人我地冇野可以再輸 我地贏嘅係年青冇負擔 我地可以慢慢一齊進步一齊守護我地認識嘅香港🇭🇰<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港，時代革命<br />\n#香港人，反抗<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n後記：<br />\n朋友唔好氣餒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至少重有我同你哋一齊肩並肩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊守護香港！<br />\n打狗救人！<br />\n前線唔係condom<br />\n<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n香港人，反抗！"},{"pid":"ff4f78c0a13f20213d85fd7bd4a7a9a50329633c","tid":1663823,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f04e73d7cb8c9c2153f69dc85055a20240e3708","tid":1663823,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff4f78c0a13f20213d85fd7bd4a7a9a50329633c","tid":1663823,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:02:22.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你點做到的"},{"pid":"6e9246442cacd54cfcd117d9e5144be83c28173a","tid":1663823,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"我都準備升級了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGjvKmq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGjvKmq.gif&h=f48ce723&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d684086d4d3efb41edeb3d029843586b461e4699","tid":1663823,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9246442cacd54cfcd117d9e5144be83c28173a","tid":1663823,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"我都準備升級了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qGjvKmq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqGjvKmq.gif&h=f48ce723&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:07:03.000Z","msg":"一齊補充人口流失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a1282b55d3397616a32e5e23a8510840a8bf8b","tid":1663823,"uid":296712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"負評果啲同我出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog